---

<section class="section moat-section">
  <div class="container moat-layout">
    <div class="moat-card">
      <div class="eyebrow">Why Ube</div>
      <h2 class="t-display-lg publisher-section-title">
        No ad platform will tell you to spend less on its own platform.
      </h2>
      <p class="t-body-md body">
        Meta will not shift budget to Google. Apple will not tune your Play
        Console listing. RevenueCat and AdMob live in different lanes. Ube
        has no platform of its own to favor — its only incentive is your
        app's success.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="moat-matrix" aria-hidden="true">
      <div><span>Meta</span><strong>Paid Media</strong></div>
      <div><span>RevenueCat</span><strong>Subscriptions</strong></div>
      <div><span>AdMob</span><strong>Ad Inventory</strong></div>
      <div><span>Ube</span><strong>Whole app math</strong></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .moat-section {
    background: var(--canvas-soft);
    border-block: 1px solid var(--hairline-soft);
  }
  .moat-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.82fr) minmax(420px, 1fr);
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .publisher-section-title {
    margin: 18px 0 0;
    max-width: 840px;
  }
  .moat-card {
    max-width: 650px;
  }
  .moat-card p {
    margin: 22px 0 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .moat-matrix {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .moat-matrix div {
    min-height: 150px;
    padding: 18px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
  }
  .moat-matrix div:last-child {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-tint), var(--card-bg));
  }
  .moat-matrix span {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.7px;
  }
  .moat-matrix strong {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .moat-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .moat-matrix {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
